<font color="#FF0000">THE WALL</font><br>
<tt>Thu Nov 28 12:34:32 US/Eastern 1996
</tt><p>
Rodruigez, Smith... the names burn from the wall to my memory. I did not know them but their names are the ones above, below, before or after the names of the friends I lost. Their deaths no less tragic no less painful than Charlie's or Bill's. As I touch the cool polished stone I seen in the reflection  the thousands who survived, who remained, who's names are not here but who left a part of  themselves in the names.....
